{"word":"H7620 - שָׁבוּעַ - shâbûwaʻ - shaw-boo'-ah - Seven","slug":"H7620","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁבוּעַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâbûwaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-boo'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Seven"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E2;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E2;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E2; - sha&#x0302;bu&#x0302;a&#x201B;  sha&#x0302;bu&#x0302;a&#x201B;  shebu&#x0302;&#x201B;a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>shaw-boo'-ah, shaw-boo'-ah, sheb-oo-aw'</i><p/>Properly passive participle of <a href=\"#/H7650\">H7650</a> as a denominative of <a href=\"#/H7651\">H7651</a>; literally <i>sevened</i>, that is, a <i>week</i> (specifically of years): - seven, week."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7621\">H7621</a>, <a href=\"#/H7637\">H7637</a>, <a href=\"#/H7650\">H7650</a>, <a href=\"#/H7651\">H7651</a>, <a href=\"#/H7652\">H7652</a>, <a href=\"#/H7656\">H7656</a>, <a href=\"#/H7657\">H7657</a>, <a href=\"#/H7658\">H7658</a>, <a href=\"#/H7659\">H7659</a>"}]}